title: 2021 Pop Culture Wrap Up & RHONJ Trailer Recap! (with Hannah Brown)
itunes:title: 2021 Pop Culture Wrap Up & RHONJ Trailer Recap! (with Hannah Brown)
description:
Friend of the show Hannah Brown joins Danny for a trailer recap of The Real Housewives of New Jersey, and the two say goodbye to 2021 with thoughts on the biggest pop culture stories of the year (according to Cafe Mom)! PS this is the VERY LAST episode recorded in the construction-filled hell of Danny's old apartment, so apologies for the background noise, but know that it's the very last time you'll hear it! :) Happy 2022!
